</td>
<td>Processing is based on legal obligations.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><b>Retention period: </b>In accordance with national law in respective country.&nbsp;</p>
<h4>Handling of customer service inquiries</h4>
<p>We may process your Personal Data in order to respond to, assist, follow up and handle your customer service inquiry. This includes communication necessary in order for us to respond to questions you have submitted to us via telephone, e-mail, social media or other communication channel. We may also process your Personal Data in order to handle complaints or support inquiries, including technical support.</p>
<table border="0">
